laboratory_examinations.findings: Appendix dilated at the base measuring up to 12 mm, appendiceal wall thickening and mucosal enhancement, edema and stranding in the fat adjacent to the appendix, adjacent terminal ileum demonstrates mild wall enhancement and thickening. No acute abnormalities in visualized lung bases, normal heart base, liver, gallbladder, biliary tree, spleen, pancreas, adrenal glands, kidneys; no biliary dilation, no free fluid or air in the abdomen.
